  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In order to improve the investigators knowledge about uveitis and the underlying mechanism of
      disease, the investigators propose collecting blood from patients with uveitis, isolating DNA
      and sequencing the DNA to identify genetic mutations or associations in these patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
