  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Non infectious uveitis</measure>
    <time_frame>5 years</time_frame>
    <description>Distinct uveitis conditions will have a polymorphism association or specific mutation.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Infectious uveitis</measure>
    <time_frame>5 years</time_frame>
    <description>Infectious uveitis (such as herpes associated uveitis, toxoplasmosis retinochoroiditis) will have specific polymorphisms/mutations in innate immune system genes which predispose the patient to infectious uveitis.</description>
  </secondary_outcome>
